Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.85,0:15:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Droga, ela só ficou em segundo.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.19,0:15:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,O que é isso?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.31,0:15:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,O Simulador de RV.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.65,0:15:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Espera, Nagate!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.03,0:15:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ei, olha.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.32,0:15:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,É o novo aluno.
